VIDEO: Šok v nakupovalnem središču: na sebi je imela le ...
Playboyeva zajčica je pripravila umetniški nastop.
01 Nov 2019, 17:34 by M. U.



Prelepa bivša zajčica. FOTO: Instagram



Čudovita telesna poslikava. FOTO: Instagram


Francia James je nekdanja Playboyeva zajčica iz Kolumbije, zdaj pa živi v Miamiju. Nedavno se je v tamkajšnjem nabito polnem trgovskem centru že navsezgodaj pojavila oblečena le v tangice.



Na sebi je imela še poslikavo Spider-Mana. Seveda to ne bi imelo nobenega smisla, če ne bi bilo objavljeno, več kot pol milijona ogledov na instagramu pa ji dokazuje, da se je odločila prav.

VIDEO: Shopping Mall Shock: She Only Wore ...
Playboy Bunny put on an art show.
01 Nov 2019, 17:34 by M. U.



Beautiful ex-bunny. PHOTO: Instagram



Wonderful body painting. PHOTO: Instagram


Francia James is a former Playboy bunny from Columbia, and now lives in Miami. Recently, a thong wearing a full shopping mall has appeared all the time.



She also had a Spider-Man painting on her. Of course, this wouldn't make any sense if it wasn't posted, and more than half a million instagram views prove to her that she's made the right decision.
